<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 14:07:29 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>犹太机构拒绝在耶路撒冷骄傲游行期间悬挂 LGBTQ 旗帜的请求</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/jewish-agency-rejects-plea-to-fly-lgbtq-flag-during-jerusalems-pride-parade/0000018f-bf03-dfeb-a58f-bffb61590000</link><description>这一请求的灵感来自于犹太复国主义大会通过的“历史性决议”，该决议“支持全世界 LGBTQ 群体与以色列之间的联系”。在拒绝后，犹太机构重申，它“每天都尊重并包容[其]社区的所有成员”</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 13:29:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/jewish-agency-rejects-plea-to-fly-lgbtq-flag-during-jerusalems-pride-parade/0000018f-bf03-dfeb-a58f-bffb61590000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡是否会在梅洛尼领导的意大利失去一个重要的右翼盟友？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/is-netanyahu-losing-a-key-right-wing-ally-in-melonis-italy/0000018f-bece-d5c5-a3ff-ffeff8270000</link><description>意大利总理乔治亚·梅洛尼是 10 月 7 日之后首批公开支持以色列的世界领导人之一。现在，就连她也与以色列总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡保持距离，并公开谈论巴勒斯坦国</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 13:26:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/is-netanyahu-losing-a-key-right-wing-ally-in-melonis-italy/0000018f-bece-d5c5-a3ff-ffeff8270000</guid></item><item><title>礼貌的以色列定居者礼貌地剥夺巴勒斯坦人的财产</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/the-polite-israeli-settlers-who-courteously-dispossess-palestinians/0000018f-ba79-d19e-a19f-fefb8c710000</link><description>在西岸的一些地区，穿着军装的定居者在驱逐农地所有者的同时避免暴力</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 12:57:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/the-polite-israeli-settlers-who-courteously-dispossess-palestinians/0000018f-ba79-d19e-a19f-fefb8c710000</guid></item><item><title>“我会把他们赶出去”：特朗普告诉犹太捐助者他将驱逐亲巴勒斯坦抗议者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/i-will-throw-them-out-trump-tells-jewish-donors-hell-deport-pro-palestinian-protesters/0000018f-bebb-d19e-a19f-fefb8d910000</link><description>在与捐助者的闭门会议上，特朗普承诺如果当选，将迅速对学生抗议者采取行动，同时确认以色列有权进行“反恐战争”，这与之前呼吁结束战争的声明相矛盾</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 11:34:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/i-will-throw-them-out-trump-tells-jewish-donors-hell-deport-pro-palestinian-protesters/0000018f-bebb-d19e-a19f-fefb8d910000</guid></item><item><title>德国裔以色列人入籍申请激增</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/naturalization-applications-surge-from-israelis-with-german-roots/0000018f-be7f-d19e-a19f-feff477d0000</link><description>报告显示，今年1月至4月共收到6,869份申请，而2023年全年收到9,129份申请，2022年收到5,670份申请</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 09:59:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/naturalization-applications-surge-from-israelis-with-german-roots/0000018f-be7f-d19e-a19f-feff477d0000</guid></item><item><title>总检察长称，本-格维尔传唤谴责以色列警察局长是非法的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/hearing-ben-gvir-is-set-to-hold-for-israels-police-chief-is-illegal-ag-says/0000018f-be36-df6b-a3ff-fe3eaecd0000</link><description>总检察长表示，传唤警察局长引发了人们的担忧，因为本-格维尔试图惩罚他，因为他阻止他干预警察工作，这与高等法院的裁决相矛盾。她写道：“有人担心你想以他为榜样来威慑整个警察指挥链。”</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 09:53:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/hearing-ben-gvir-is-set-to-hold-for-israels-police-chief-is-illegal-ag-says/0000018f-be36-df6b-a3ff-fe3eaecd0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙的死亡人数实际上比报道的要高</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/rising-fatality-numbers-in-gaza-are-in-all-probability-higher-than-reported/0000018f-bab5-de04-a58f-bab5ea1d0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 09:38:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/rising-fatality-numbers-in-gaza-are-in-all-probability-higher-than-reported/0000018f-bab5-de04-a58f-bab5ea1d0000</guid></item><item><title>阿拉伯国家恳求欧盟高级官员承认巴勒斯坦国</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/arab-states-implore-senior-eu-officials-to-recognize-a-palestinian-state/0000018f-be1b-df6b-a3ff-fe3b5e0a0000</link><description>多个阿拉伯国家的高级官员在布鲁塞尔举行会谈，呼吁欧盟国家加入爱尔兰、挪威和西班牙的声明，并对以色列对美国与沙特阿拉伯的正常化协议大纲的反应表示失望</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 08:27:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/arab-states-implore-senior-eu-officials-to-recognize-a-palestinian-state/0000018f-be1b-df6b-a3ff-fe3b5e0a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列袭击拉法后，致命大火在加沙人中蔓延绝望和悲伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/deadly-fire-spreads-despair-grief-among-gazans-after-israeli-strike/0000018f-be05-d475-a5cf-feffa1ee0000</link><description>加沙卫生当局称，有 45 人死亡，其中大部分是妇女、儿童和老人。一名难民营居民说：“在巴勒斯坦，我们的孩子、长辈、妇女和家园每天都在燃烧”</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 07:37:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/deadly-fire-spreads-despair-grief-among-gazans-after-israeli-strike/0000018f-be05-d475-a5cf-feffa1ee0000</guid></item><item><title>个性化噬菌体疗法治愈了从三层楼摔下来的耶路撒冷猫</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/science-and-health/2024-05-28/ty-article-magazine/cat-in-jerusalem-who-fell-three-stories-healed-with-personalized-bacteriophage-therapy/0000018f-ba3e-dca9-a5cf-be3ee4360000</link><description>暹罗猫“吱吱”地折断了两条后腿，一条腿被截肢，另一条腿的植入物遭受了慢性感染。进入高科技医学领域，进行人体测试</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 06:28:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/science-and-health/2024-05-28/ty-article-magazine/cat-in-jerusalem-who-fell-three-stories-healed-with-personalized-bacteriophage-therapy/0000018f-ba3e-dca9-a5cf-be3ee4360000</guid></item><item><title>资料来源：以色列国防军内部报告发现两名加沙人在前往以色列监狱的途中被殴打死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/sources-idf-report-finds-two-gazans-died-after-being-beaten-en-route-to-israeli-prison/0000018f-bbbb-df3d-abbf-bffb68980000</link><description>被拘留者正在前往斯德泰曼拘留所的途中，其中大多数人都在那里。虽然几名士兵就此事件接受讯问，但没有人因涉嫌造成死亡而被捕</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 05:26:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/sources-idf-report-finds-two-gazans-died-after-being-beaten-en-route-to-israeli-prison/0000018f-bbbb-df3d-abbf-bffb68980000</guid></item><item><title>寻求庇护者在特拉维夫厄立特里亚政权支持者与反对者之间的斗殴中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/asylum-seeker-killed-in-tel-aviv-brawl-between-supporters-opponents-of-eritrean-regime/0000018f-bd3c-d5c5-a3ff-fd3d3f070000</link><description>以色列警方在特拉维夫南部逮捕了数十人。本月早些时候，一名反对厄立特里亚政权的寻求庇护者在同一地点的一场斗殴中被谋杀</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 03:32:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/asylum-seeker-killed-in-tel-aviv-brawl-between-supporters-opponents-of-eritrean-regime/0000018f-bd3c-d5c5-a3ff-fd3d3f070000</guid></item><item><title>加沙卫生官员报告以色列对拉法帐篷区的新袭击造成 21 人死亡、数十人受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-28/ty-article-live/un-security-council-to-hold-emergency-session-after-mass-civilian-causalities-in-rafah/0000018f-bd07-d5c5-a3ff-fd2fd64a0000</link><description>据报道，以色列坦克抵达拉法市中心 ■ 近东救济工程处称，过去三周内约有一百万人逃离拉法 ■ 美国广播公司新闻报道，一块弹片点燃了一个油箱，导致拉法起火 ■ 爱尔兰、西班牙、挪威正式承认一名巴勒斯坦人状态</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 02:34:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-28/ty-article-live/un-security-council-to-hold-emergency-session-after-mass-civilian-causalities-in-rafah/0000018f-bd07-d5c5-a3ff-fd2fd64a0000</guid></item><item><title>大棒而非胡萝卜：国际刑事法院之争表明全球对顽固的以色列不耐烦</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-27/ty-article-opinion/.premium/sticks-not-carrots-icc-battle-signals-global-impatience-with-intransigent-israel/0000018f-baad-df3d-abbf-bffd33e30000</link><description>就连以色列的盟友也不认为其政府能够应对加沙战争，这促使以色列采取制裁定居者、冻结军事援助等行动，现在还可能对以色列的拉法行动发出国际刑事法院的逮捕令和国际法院的命令</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 20:37:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-27/ty-article-opinion/.premium/sticks-not-carrots-icc-battle-signals-global-impatience-with-intransigent-israel/0000018f-baad-df3d-abbf-bffd33e30000</guid></item><item><title>即使没有人质协议，拉法的平民死亡也可能迫使以色列停火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article/.premium/civilian-deaths-in-rafah-could-force-israel-into-a-cease-fire-even-without-a-hostage-deal/0000018f-bba5-d5c5-a3ff-fbad95c50000</link><description>以色列国防军正在向城市推进，但即使是强制撤离也没有解决密集地区的作战问题，看来部队的压力是行动的主要困难</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 20:23:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article/.premium/civilian-deaths-in-rafah-could-force-israel-into-a-cease-fire-even-without-a-hostage-deal/0000018f-bba5-d5c5-a3ff-fbad95c50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列新征兵部队被派往加沙贾巴利亚，只受过最低限度的训练</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-new-israeli-army-conscripts-sent-to-gazas-jabalya-with-minimal-training/0000018f-bb40-dc1f-abef-ff79e0270000</link><description>“他们到达时有点震惊，但几天后，爆炸就成了家常便饭”：当新武装的以色列国防军新兵通常仍在训练时，他们现在发现自己身处加沙战场的中心</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 20:07:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-new-israeli-army-conscripts-sent-to-gazas-jabalya-with-minimal-training/0000018f-bb40-dc1f-abef-ff79e0270000</guid></item><item><title>欧洲外交官警告拉法罢工将加大对以色列接受停火的压力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article/.premium/european-diplomats-warn-rafah-strike-could-lead-to-strict-interpretation-of-icj-orders/0000018f-bb65-d5c5-a3ff-fb6dd0720000</link><description>尽管国际法院上周限制以色列在拉法行动的命令“足够模糊，足以让各国能够视而不见”，但欧洲外交官警告说，以色列从夜间到周一对拉法的致命袭击可能会改变局面</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 19:35:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article/.premium/european-diplomats-warn-rafah-strike-could-lead-to-strict-interpretation-of-icj-orders/0000018f-bb65-d5c5-a3ff-fb6dd0720000</guid></item><item><title>庆祝拉法巴勒斯坦人死亡的右翼分子是以色列的“真面目”吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-27/ty-article/.highlight/are-right-wingers-celebrating-palestinian-deaths-in-rafah-the-true-face-of-israel/0000018f-baee-dfb0-a7af-fbfe52ac0000</link><description>有人说，这才是以色列真正的丑恶嘴脸。那些相信并且了解一个不同的以色列的人面临着证明事实并非如此的不可能的挑战</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 19:20:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-27/ty-article/.highlight/are-right-wingers-celebrating-palestinian-deaths-in-rafah-the-true-face-of-israel/0000018f-baee-dfb0-a7af-fbfe52ac0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列电视曝光揭露内塔尼亚胡主要部长涉嫌严重腐败</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-tv-expose-uncovers-alleged-deep-corruption-of-key-netanyahu-minister/0000018f-bab5-d0b7-abdf-feb7c40f0000</link><description>以色列警察和总检察长等众多观众热切观看了交通部长米里·雷格夫的两集电视特别节目，并宣布他们正在调查她在任期间的行为</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 17:47:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-tv-expose-uncovers-alleged-deep-corruption-of-key-netanyahu-minister/0000018f-bab5-d0b7-abdf-feb7c40f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列极右翼部长本-格维尔传唤警察局长进行谴责，尽管他无权这样做</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article/israeli-minister-ben-gvir-summons-top-cop-for-reprimand-despite-lacking-authority-to-do-so/0000018f-baf5-d19e-a19f-fef734af0000</link><description>以色列国家安全部长在给该专员的一封信中声称，“最近对你总体功能失调的指控越来越多”，并补充说，“你唯一做得好的事情就是提拔与你关系密切的官员”</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 17:22:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article/israeli-minister-ben-gvir-summons-top-cop-for-reprimand-despite-lacking-authority-to-do-so/0000018f-baf5-d19e-a19f-fef734af0000</guid></item></channel></rss>